<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Proposal Viewed</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #f59e0b; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background: #f9fafb; }
        .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
        .info { background: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #f59e0b; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üëÅÔ∏è Proposal Viewed</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello {{senderName}},</h2>
            
            <div class="info">
                <h3>Your proposal has been viewed!</h3>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h3>{{proposalTitle}}</h3>
                <p><strong>Viewed by:</strong> {{viewerName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Viewed on:</strong> {{viewedDate}}</p>
                <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{status}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>This notification lets you know that your proposal has been opened and reviewed.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{proposalLink}}" class="button" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #f59e0b; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">View Proposal</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>You will be notified when any action is taken on this proposal.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent by the Proposal Management System</p>
            <p>¬© 2024 Proposal Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
